-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; white-space: nowrap;&quot;&gt;IMPORTE FINAL DEL EXTRACTO&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl657&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; white-space: nowrap; text-align: right;&quot;&gt;17,2&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl325&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; white-space: nowrap;&quot;&gt;Numérico Sig. Cero&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl325&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; white-space: nowrap;&quot;&gt;Salida&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;370&quot; class=&quot;xl658&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: top; border: 0.5pt solid black; width: 278pt;&quot;&gt;Se obtiene en la rutina ATR017, IMPINI (MPDT182) - IMPFAC (MPDT012). El IMPFAC se obtiene por CODENT, CENTALTA, CUENTA, CLAMON, NUMEXTCTA+1, TIPOFAC (288) y INDMOVANU (0)&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;195&quot; class=&quot;xl653&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: top; border: 0.5pt solid black; width: 146pt;&quot;&gt;Saldo final del extracto&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr height=&quot;186&quot; style=&quot;height: 139.5pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;td height=&quot;186&quot; class=&quot;xl325&quot; align=&quot;right&quot; style=&quot;padding-top: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; vertical-align: middle; border: 0.5pt solid black; white-space: nowrap; height: 139.5pt;&quot;&gt;11&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;xl656&quot; style=&qu